                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d718">
                <head>No. 716.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Ball</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Havana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-11-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">Nov</hi>. 5, 1873</date>. (Received Nov. 5—5.20
                        p.m.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>An official bulletin announces the capture of the steamer Virginius, October 31,
                    toward the coast of Jamaica; it further states that a competent tribunal is
                    trying the prisoners, whom it styles pirates.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>HALL.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
